   <documentation>Test cases are methods of the Test unit.

The tests descriptions are used to generate low level documentation of the project. Therefore they should be a full declarative sentence.

Checking that the description is indeed covers the functionality checked by the unit test is a central element of the review process.
</documentation>
</element>
